Twenty people have been injured after a plane had a crash landing at Hiroshima .
There were believed to be 74 passengers and seven crew members on board Asiana Airlines flight OZ162 when it was reported to have made a tailstrike and skidded off the runway .
Japanese media are reporting the plane spun 180 degrees after impact to be left facing the wrong way on runway .
